The paper deals with a machine learning problem, specifically Symbolic Regression, which involves finding a mathematical expression that describes the relationship between variables. This falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new data structure and heuristic to improve the search process, which could fall under the categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of the algorithm for decision-making, which could fall under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
